'''evolution'''

# The [[gradual]] [[process]] by which something [[evolve]]s to a different, often more [[complex]], [[form]].
# {{biology}} the change in the [[genetic]] [[composition]] of a [[population]] in successive [[generation]]s.
# {{mathematics}} the [[extraction]] of a [[root]] of a [[quantity]].

